00:29:41.580 --> 00:29:45.690
to these PWA experiences.

00:29:45.690 --> 00:29:49.290
They also offer a new
sign in experience

00:29:49.290 --> 00:29:51.720
that enables web sessions
to persist much longer

00:29:51.720 --> 00:29:54.600
than before, similar
to with native apps,

00:29:54.600 --> 00:29:59.100
so users don't have to log in
as often into your experience.

00:29:59.100 --> 00:30:01.830
And they integrate with
the new web payments

00:30:01.830 --> 00:30:05.790
API, which gives us
a powerful new way

00:30:05.790 --> 00:30:09.240
to make buying things through
a web browser really friction

00:30:09.240 --> 00:30:12.630
free and really easy.

00:30:12.630 --> 00:30:17.940
In addition to these benefits,
PWAs use HDTPS all the time

00:30:17.940 --> 00:30:20.010
for enhanced security.

00:30:20.010 --> 00:30:21.870
And if you do it
right, they can have

00:30:21.870 --> 00:30:25.650
buttery smooth, 60
frames per second updates

00:30:25.650 --> 00:30:28.530
to your user interface, which
makes them really, really

00:30:28.530 --> 00:30:29.610
fun to use.

00:30:29.610 --> 00:30:33.030
And they can resize
gracefully to displays

00:30:33.030 --> 00:30:35.460
of all shapes and sizes.

00:30:35.460 --> 00:30:41.850
PWAs are truly the next
generation of the web.

00:30:41.850 --> 00:30:46.260
Developers who have made PWAs
are seeing great results.

