of the art for our industry

00:56:39.440 --> 00:56:42.680
by many, many years.

00:56:42.680 --> 00:56:47.060
And I'm thrilled that we've made
the same ML framework that we

00:56:47.060 --> 00:56:50.540
use internally at
Google available to you

00:56:50.540 --> 00:56:54.194
