project called TensorFlow.

00:56:57.990 --> 00:57:02.040
TensorFlow works by giving you
a way to define a data model,

00:57:02.040 --> 00:57:06.030
and then use that model to
analyze large amounts of data.

00:57:06.030 --> 00:57:09.120
